OL,3,CCouple accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cdaughter begin trial at Stafford Court
OL,6,FThis article contains details that
OL,7,Fsome readers may find distressing
OL,9,FTwo parents have gone on trial accused
OL,10,Fof killing their five-week-old
OL,11,Fdaughter.
OL,13,FSean Jefferson, 35 from Walsall, and
OL,14,FAmy Clark, 34 from Lichfield, are said
OL,15,Fto have either violently shaken their
OL,16,Fdaughter, or struck her head against a
OL,17,Fsurface.
OL,19,FDarcy-Leigh Jefferson died on 29 March
OL,20,F2022, having been born prematurely
OL,21,Fjust five weeks earlier.
