OL,3,CCouple accused of murdering baby
OL,4,Cdaughter begin trial at Stafford Court
OL,6,FThe trial against the pair opened this
OL,7,Fmorning at Stafford Crown Court. It
OL,8,Fheard how Darcy-Leigh's body displayed
OL,9,F47 rib fractures that had been caused
OL,10,Fby at least three separate incidents
OL,11,Fof physical abuse.
OL,13,FAt least three of those fractures were
OL,14,Fcaused on at least one occasion in the
OL,15,Ffirst couple of weeks of her life.
OL,17,FThe prosecution allege that 11 of the
OL,18,Frib fractures may have been caused on
OL,19,Fthe same occasion that the fatal head
OL,20,Finjury was.
