OL,6,FBoth Jefferson and Clark were in court
OL,7,Fto hear the opening statement in their
OL,8,Ftrial.
OL,10,FSitting a couple of metres apart, they
OL,11,Fheard details of their characters and
OL,12,Frelationship set out.
OL,14,FThe court was told how Amy Clarke
OL,15,Fdrank and took drugs, namely cocaine,
OL,16,Fduring her pregnancy with Darcy-Leigh,
OL,17,Fwhilst Sean Jefferson used cannabis.
