OL,6,FHe was aware of Amy's drink and drug
OL,7,Fuse, sending messages including one
OL,8,Fthat said: "I kicked off cuz u been
OL,9,Fsniffing coke and drinking all night
OL,10,Fwhile your pregnant."
OL,12,FTheir relationship was described by a
OL,13,Ffriend as "toxic" and the court were
OL,14,Fshown a number of messages between the
OL,15,Fcouple which demonstrated the
OL,16,Fvolatility.
OL,18,FThese included one where Amy texted
OL,19,FSean saying "u threatening to beat me
OL,20,Fup while I have our daughter in my
OL,21,Farms..."
