OL,6,FProsecturos claim both defendants knew
OL,7,Fthere was a "risk of the other flying
OL,8,Foff the handle" and therefore they
OL,9,Fknew "there was a significant risk of
OL,10,Fthe other causing serious psychical
OL,11,Fharm to Darcy-Leigh, especially when
OL,12,Falcohol and drugs were involved."
OL,14,FDarcy-Leigh was seen by health
OL,15,Fprofessionals on a number of occasions
OL,16,Fand no concerns were identified until
OL,17,Fa couple of days before she was
OL,18,Fadmitted to hospital with serious
OL,19,Finjures.
