OL,6,FThe court also heard that because of
OL,7,Fsocial services involvement, Darcy-
OL,8,FLeigh should have been registered on a
OL,9,Fchild protection sharing system. An
OL,10,Ferror meant she wasn't.
OL,12,FThe prosecution will continue setting
OL,13,Fout their case when the trial
OL,14,Fcontinues on Monday.
OL,16,FBoth Sean Jefferson and Amy Clarke
OL,17,Fdeny murder and causing or allowing
OL,18,Fthe death of a child.
